resolution-op equals
resolution-value PASS
resolution-fallback __KICK_RESULT__ PASS witness=<path> tier1>0 falsifier_pass>0
why "User directive 무결점 100% 까지 폐쇄루프 cron — converge to defect-zero kick PASS state via parallel sub-agent fix dispatch. Closes 5 audit-identified bugs P1-P5."
omega-stop fixpoint-convergence
deps raw:omega-blocker-autofire raw:problem-solving-triad raw:proof-carrying
classifier-version closed-loop-defect-zero.v1
note "Cron 73dd3421 fires every 5min. Self-terminates on __KICK_RESULT__ PASS via CronDelete. Bug priority P1-P5 from sub-agent C audit (2026-04-28)."
